messages.content: I'm at Valparaiso University, about an hour  away from Chicago. And I wanna teach math - middle school or high school math
Thanks man. And that's cool! Which school and what do you want to teach? We should definitely catch up when you are in town
I'm doing great. I'm in northern Indiana trying to get a teaching degree. Maybe we can catch up some time if I'm back in Ypsi. Congrats on the marriage!
Hey Andy! Great to hear from you. I'm doing well how are you?
